{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[E]People come, [A]people go
[E]Some grow young, [A]some grow cold_(harmonica: E . A . E . A .)
[E]I woke up [A]in between
A [E]memory [A]and a dream_(harmonica: E . A . E . A .)
{end_of_verse}


{start_of_part: Pre-Chorus}
